---
import { SITE_URL } from '@lib/config';
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEO from '@components/seo/SEO.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@components/layout/Breadcrumb.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'June 20, 2026';
const title = 'Terms of Service — Scrabble Word Finder';
const description =
  'Terms of Service for Scrabble Word Finder. Learn about our terms of use, API guidelines, disclaimer of warranties, and advertising policies.';
const canonical = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, SITE_URL).href;
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEO slot="head" title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} />

  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Terms of Service' }]} />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mb-4 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans',system-ui,sans-serif] animate-entrance"
      >
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] animate-entrance delay-1">
        Last Updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Terms Content -->
    <div class="card p-8 md:p-10 animate-entrance delay-2">
      <div
        class="prose-content
        [&>p]:text-base [&>p]:leading-relaxed [&>p]:text-[var(--color-text-main)] [&>p]:mb-5
        [&>h2]:font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans',system-ui,sans-serif] [&>h2]:text-xl [&>h2]:font-bold [&>h2]:text-[var(--color-text-main)] [&>h2]:mt-8 [&>h2]:mb-3
        [&>h3]:font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans',system-ui,sans-serif] [&>h3]:text-lg [&>h3]:font-bold [&>h3]:text-[var(--color-text-main)] [&>h3]:mt-6 [&>h3]:mb-2
        [&>ul]:list-disc [&>ul]:pl-6 [&>ul]:mb-5 [&>ul]:space-y-1.5 [&>ul]:text-[var(--color-text-main)]
        [&>a]:text-[var(--color-primary)] [&>a]:underline [&>a]:hover:opacity-80 [&>a]:transition-opacity"
      >
        <p>
          Welcome to ScrabbleWordFinder.com (the "Website"). By accessing or using our Website,
          tools, and services (collectively, the "Service"), you agree to comply with and be bound
          by the following Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use
          our Service.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Entertainment Use Only</h2>
        <p>
          Our word finder, anagram solver, and dictionary checker tools are provided solely for
          entertainment, educational, and casual play purposes. We aim to support your word game
          practice, vocabulary building, and friendly matches.
        </p>

        <h2>2. No Warranty on Word Validity</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to maintain accurate, up-to-date databases based on official word lists
          (such as TWL, SOWPODS, and ENABLE), we provide the Service "as is" and "as available." We
          make no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, regarding the
          completeness, accuracy, reliability, or validity of any word, score, or definition
          generated by the Service. Your use of the Service is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Advertisements</h2>
        <p>
          To keep our tools free to the public, the Service displays third-party advertisements.
          These ads help cover hosting, database maintenance, and API costs. By using the Website,
          you acknowledge and agree that ads will be displayed. Please refer to our Privacy Policy
          for more information on how our advertising partners handle user data.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Trademark Disclaimer & Non-Affiliation</h2>
        <p>
          SCRABBLE ® is a registered trademark. All intellectual property rights in and to the game
          are owned in the U.S.A. by Hasbro, Inc., in Canada by Hasbro Canada, Inc., and throughout
          the rest of the world, by J.W. Spear & Sons, PLC of Enfield, Middlesex, England, a
          subsidiary of Mattel Inc. Mattel & Spear are not affiliated with Hasbro or Hasbro Canada.
          Words With Friends is a trademark of Zynga. ScrabbleWordFinder.com is an independent
          reference utility and is not affiliated with, associated with, sponsored by, or endorsed
          by Hasbro, Mattel, Zynga, or any of their partners. All trademarks used on this site
          remain the property of their respective owners.
        </p>

        <h2>5. API Usage and Abuse Prevention</h2>
        <p>
          You agree not to abuse, disrupt, or harm our Service or its underlying application
          programming interfaces (APIs). Specifically, you must not:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Use any automated scraping, crawling, bots, or scripts to access or copy our database of
            words, points, or definitions.
          </li>
          <li>
            Submit an excessive volume of requests to our API endpoints (such as search or
            check-word endpoints) in a manner that degrades performance for other users.
          </li>
          <li>
            Attempt to bypass our rate limiters or security controls. We reserve the right to block,
            restrict, or suspend access to our Service for any IP address or user violating these
            terms.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update or modify these Terms of Service at any time. When we make
          material changes, we will: (a) revise the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page, and
          (b) post a prominent notice on our homepage for at least 30 days after changes take
          effect. Your continued use of the Service after any changes constitutes your acceptance of
          the new terms. If you do not agree to the new terms, you must stop using the Service.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, IN NO EVENT SHALL
          SCRABBLEWORDFINDER.COM, ITS DEVELOPERS, OFFICERS, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, OR AGENTS BE
          LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES,
          INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE
          LOSSES, RESULTING FROM YOUR ACCESS TO OR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO ACCESS OR USE) THE
          SERVICE.
        </p>
        <p>
          IN NO EVENT SHALL OUR AGGREGATE LIABILITY TO YOU FOR ALL CLAIMS ARISING FROM OR RELATED TO
          YOUR USE OF THE SERVICE EXCEED THE GREATER OF (A) THE AMOUNT YOU PAID TO US IN THE TWELVE
          (12) MONTHS PRIOR TO THE EVENT GIVING RISE TO THE LIABILITY, OR (B) ONE HUNDRED UNITED
          STATES DOLLARS (USD $100.00).
        </p>
        <p>
          SOME JURISDICTIONS DO NOT ALLOW THE EXCLUSION OR LIMITATION OF LIABILITY FOR CONSEQUENTIAL
          OR INCIDENTAL DAMAGES, SO THE ABOVE LIMITATION MAY NOT APPLY TO YOU.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless ScrabbleWordFinder.com and its
          affiliates, officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any claims,
          liabilities, damages, losses, and expenses, including reasonable attorneys' fees, arising
          out of or in any way connected with: (a) your access to or use of the Service; (b) your
          violation of these Terms; (c) your violation of any third-party right, including any
          intellectual property right or privacy right; or (d) any claim that your use of our
          Service caused damage to a third party.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms of Service and your use of the Service shall be governed by and construed in
          accordance with the laws of the State of Delaware, without regard to its conflict of law
          principles. Any legal action or proceeding arising under these Terms of Service shall be
          brought exclusively in the federal or state courts located in Delaware.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
